<!--
布局：account/auth - 登录/注册等认证页面
兼容 layoutType=account.auth 的路径解析；顶栏底栏与首页同源（Theme Partials）。

字段
@meta.name {default="账号认证布局",name="账号认证布局",description="登录注册等认证页布局"}
@meta.description {default="Partials 顶栏底栏与首页一致",name="描述",description="顶栏底栏与首页一致"}
@preview.login {default=0,option={0:不需要登录,1:需要登录},name="是否需要登录",description="认证页通常不需要已登录"}
@param.title {default="登录",name="页面标题",description="页面标题"}
@param.content {default="",name="主要内容",description="认证表单等内容"}
@param.class {default="",name="额外CSS类",description="根节点额外 class"}
@param.showHeader {default=false,name="是否显示header",description="认证页默认不渲染商城顶栏"}
@param.showFooter {default=false,name="是否显示footer",description="认证页默认不渲染商城底栏"}
@param.showSearch {default=true,name="顶栏搜索",description="顶栏是否展示搜索（Partials）"}
@param.showUserMenu {default=true,name="用户菜单",description="顶栏是否展示用户菜单（Partials）"}

参数由 ControllerFetchFileBefore Observer 合并进 meta
-->
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="{{htmlLang}}" dir="{{htmlDir}}" data-local="{{lang_local}}" data-lang="{{lang}}" data-dir="{{htmlDir}}">
<head>
    <?php
    $meta = $this->getData('meta') ?? [];
    if (!is_array($meta)) {
        $meta = [];
    }
    $pageTitle = trim((string)($this->getData('title') ?: ($meta['title'] ?? __('登录'))));
    $pageDescription = trim((string)($this->getData('description') ?: ($meta['description'] ?? '')));
    $contentTemplate = (string)($this->getData('meta.contentTemplate') ?: $this->getData('contentTemplate') ?: $meta['contentTemplate'] ?? '');
    $normalizedContentTemplate = str_replace('\\', '/', $contentTemplate);
    $isLoginAuthPage = str_contains($normalizedContentTemplate, '/account/login.phtml')
        || str_contains($normalizedContentTemplate, '/customer/login.phtml');
    $isDev = defined('DEV') && DEV;
    $apiWorkerUrl = $isDev
        ? '/Weline/Frontend/view/statics/js/weline-api-worker.js'
        : '/static/Weline/Frontend/js/weline-api-worker.js';
    $themeAssetVersion = '20260609-auth-api-runtime';
    $welineScriptUrl = $isDev
        ? '/Weline/Frontend/view/statics/js/weline.js?v=' . $themeAssetVersion
        : '/static/Weline/Frontend/js/weline.js?v=' . $themeAssetVersion;
    ?>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title><?= htmlspecialchars($pageTitle !== '' ? $pageTitle : (string)__('登录'), ENT_QUOTES, 'UTF-8') ?></title>
    <?php if ($pageDescription !== ''): ?>
        <meta name="description" content="<?= htmlspecialchars($pageDescription, ENT_QUOTES, 'UTF-8') ?>">
    <?php endif; ?>
    <script data-no-extract="true" data-auth-runtime-config>
        (function() {
            window.WelineApiConfig = window.WelineApiConfig || {};
            window.WelineApiConfig.workerUrl = window.WelineApiConfig.workerUrl || <?= json_encode($apiWorkerUrl, JSON_UNESCAPED_SLASHES | JSON_UNESCAPED_UNICODE) ?>;
            window.WelineApiConfig.baseUrl = window.WelineApiConfig.baseUrl || window.location.origin;
            window.WelineApiConfig.cartCountCookieKey = window.WelineApiConfig.cartCountCookieKey || 'weline_cart_item_count';
        })();
    </script>
    <script src="<?= htmlspecialchars($welineScriptUrl, ENT_QUOTES, 'UTF-8') ?>"></script>
    <w:block class="Weline\Theme\Block\Partials" area="frontend" type="head" default-option="default"/>
    <style data-auth-theme-vars>
        :root,
        [data-theme="light"],
        html.light,
        [data-theme="default"],
        html[data-theme="default"] {
            --auth-input-height: var(--weline-theme-control-height-lg);
            --auth-input-padding-y: var(--weline-layout-spacing-sm);
            --auth-input-radius: var(--weline-layout-radius-lg);
            --auth-input-border-width: var(--weline-theme-border-width-2);
        }

        body.account-auth-layout {
            margin: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: var(--weline-layout-surface-secondary);
            font-family: var(--weline-layout-font-family);
            font-size: var(--weline-layout-font-size-base);
            line-height: var(--weline-layout-line-height-normal);
            color: var(--weline-layout-text-primary);
            transition: background var(--weline-theme-transition-base), color var(--weline-theme-transition-base);
        }
        .weline-page-wrapper {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: var(--weline-layout-spacing-xl) var(--weline-layout-spacing-md);
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        .weline-main-content,
        .auth-container {
            width: 100%;
        }
        .account-auth-shell {
            position: relative;
            width: fit-content;
            max-width: 100%;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        @media screen and (max-width: 640px) {
            .account-auth-shell {
                width: 100%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="account-auth-layout">
    <div class="weline-page-wrapper">
        <div class="weline-main-content">
            <main class="account-auth-content <?= htmlspecialchars(($meta['class'] ?? '')) ?>" id="account-auth-content" data-layout="account_auth_content">
                <div class="auth-container">
                    <div class="account-auth-shell<?= $isLoginAuthPage ? ' auth-login-card' : '' ?>">
                        <w:slot id="content"
                                name="内容区"
                                accept="layout-account-content,layout-account-auth-content,layout-default-content,content,account-auth,auth-form"
                                reject="header,footer"
                                multiple="true"
                                position="content"
                                class="account-auth__content-root-slot">
                            <w:slot id="account-auth-content"
                                name="账号认证内容"
                                accept="layout-account-auth-content,account-auth,auth-form,content"
                                reject="header,footer"
                                multiple="true"
                                position="content"
                                class="account-auth__content-slot">
                            <?php if ($isLoginAuthPage): ?>
                                <div class="auth-login-toolbar" aria-label="<?= htmlspecialchars((string) __('登录页工具'), ENT_QUOTES) ?>">
                                    <div class="auth-login-language">
                                        <w:i18n:language:switcher for="js" />
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            <?php endif; ?>
                            <if condition="meta.content">
                                {{meta.content}}
                                <elseif condition="content"/>
                                {{content}}
                                <elseif condition="meta.contentTemplate"/>
                                <?php echo $this->fetch($this->getData("meta.contentTemplate")); ?>
                            </if>
                            </w:slot>
                        </w:slot>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </main>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
